data.description: Lots of space for everyone!! This home has a finished walkout basement with 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and an additional living area. The main living, kitchen, dining, and laundry are all on the main level, as well as a half-bath and a large walk-in pantry. Upstairs you will find a large master suite with a walk-in closet, as well as 4th bedroom, and an office with mountain views. There are beautiful hardwood floors across the main level, in-floor heat in the basement, and in the attached 2-car garage. The property includes an extra large, paved pad that allows parking for 3 vehicles. The walk-out deck boasts views of the Big Horns and the golf course! The seller will leave all new black metal fencing materials for the front yard.
